 Nigerian singer Akinmayokun Awodumila popularly referred to as Mr. May D has sustained injuries on his leg after fire broke out at his home. Mr. May D made this known on his Instagram page as he shared a photo of his right leg showing the burns around his knee and is receiving medical attention at the hospital. Sharing the photos, the singer begged his fans to say a prayer for him so he can recover and his fans took to the comment section to wish him speedy recovery.  